OL,10,CG1980FThe siege in the Iranian
OL,11,FEmbassy, London begins today. Two BBC
OL,12,FTV News employees, who were getting
OL,13,Fpress accreditation, were amongst those
OL,14,Fheld hostage. Chris Cramer (news
OL,15,Forganiser) was released after 2 days
OL,16,Fdue to illness, whilst Sim Harris
OL,17,F(sound recordist) was held until the
OL,18,Fsiege ended.
